Software Dolibarr is described as Open source solution for all around business management: Sales, Invoicing, Agenda, Stock, Purchase Orders, Emailing, Accounting, Expense report, Leave requests. Several hundreds of modules are available according to your need.With features bank_reconciliation billing_&_invoicing expense_tracking purchase_order_management tax_management. Pricing described as Free if installed "On premise".
From 9 euros / month with a Saas provider and a target audience Thanks to its modularity (several hundred of business modules), Dolibarr meets the needs of any type of business of any size.